thread.title_full: BRIEF-Artprice H1 net income swings to profit of 250,000 euros | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Artprice H1 net income swings to profit of 250,000 euros
text:
Sept 29 Artprice Com SA :
* H1 net income of 250,000 euros ($281,875) versus loss of 76,000 euros year ago
* H1 operating income 254,000 euros versus loss of 200,000 euros a year ago Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8869 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom)
